  "sections": {
    "Background": {
      "text": "Thin or fibrotic ventricular wall\nMuscle may be absent or necrotic\nAkinetic or dyskinetic wall (paradoxical ballooning)",
      "subsections": {
        "Causes": {
          "text": "Majority\nHealed transmural\nMI\n(anterior or inferior most common)\nRare\nHOCM\nChagas",
